{"tid":2033954,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Bless - 果汁－你吾係仲飲呀嘛","createTime":"2020-05-25T03:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T17:05:17.000Z","uid":164455,"like":98,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"94dc391dd8a74e2ead95db3f10b2355ef0f7ba89","tid":2033954,"uid":164455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/whatsnew/whatsnew_fa/2020_391.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfs.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fwhatsnew%2Fwhatsnew_fa%2F2020_391.html&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=f943345d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/whatsnew/whatsnew_fa/2020_391.html</a><br />\n<br />\n產品名稱：DR. DETOX - ORIGINAL<br />\n品牌：bless<br />\n原產地：香港<br />\n分銷商：Bless International Group Limited<br />\n<br />\n中心跟進一宗食物投訴，從旺角一零售點抽取上述樣本進行檢測，結果顯示，樣本含十億分之六十三的棒曲霉素，超出中心採用的行動水平十億分之五十。<br />\n<br />\n棒曲霉素大多存在於腐爛的蘋果及蘋果製品。動物研究顯示攝入大量棒曲霉素可引致肝臟、脾臟及腎臟受損，以及對免疫系統造成毒性損害。至於人類，有報告指會出現噁心、胃腸道不適及嘔吐徵狀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtHgUuj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtHgUuj.png&h=d280f958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee12cd787924454041616d706e620fd979b97109","tid":2033954,"uid":164455,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"94dc391dd8a74e2ead95db3f10b2355ef0f7ba89","tid":2033954,"uid":164455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/whatsnew/whatsnew_fa/2020_391.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfs.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fwhatsnew%2Fwhatsnew_fa%2F2020_391.html&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=f943345d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/whatsnew/whatsnew_fa/2020_391.html</a><br />\n<br />\n產品名稱：DR. DETOX - ORIGINAL<br />\n品牌：bless<br />\n原產地：香港<br />\n分銷商：Bless International Group Limited<br />\n<br />\n中心跟進一宗食物